search_results.title: About Kyle Winkler
search_results.snippet: Kyle Winkler is a practical Bible teacher, author and creator of the popular Shut Up, Devil! mobile app. He is known for his vulnerable but bold messages.

search_results.title: Kyle J. Anderson | Historian & Writer
search_results.snippet: Kyle J. Anderson is an Associate Professor at SUNY Old Westbury and the author of The Egyptian Labor Corps: Race, Space, and Place in the First World War.
